snippet.title: For Honor: Year 6 Season 2 - Curse of the Scarab Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
In the wake of the Great Cataclysm, a terrible curse descends over Heathmoor thanks to the unwitting actions of the Raider, Bolthorn. Who will save the people from this terrible fate?
Play the limited-time Justice of Pharaohs launch event and more in Year 6 Season 2: Curse of the Scarab!

Buy the game: http://ubi.li/pcy9f
Find out more: [For Honor Seasons and Updates | Ubisoft (US)|https://www.ubisoft.com/en-us/game/for-honor/seasons]
